<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <p>Dear {{ user ? user.fullName : 'Customer' }},</p>

    <p>We are plaesed to hear that your complete Deckard inquiry #{{ inquiry.inquiryNumber }} has been delivered successfully!</p>

    <p>If you have any feedback on your experience, we would love to hear from you. You can reply to this email or leave a review through your account.</p>

    <p>You can view your inquiry details here: <a href="{{ viewUrl }}">View Inquiry</a></p>

    <p>We look forward to serving you again in the future.</p>

    <p>Sincerely, The Deckard Team</p>
</body>
</html>
